{"tid":2143418,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"北戴河會議還有意義嗎？  資深傳媒人 - 潘小濤","createTime":"2020-08-07T05:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T08:09:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"744f38b61ff65263e2bf59d301bcb40eda667b7f","tid":2143418,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:36:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/TMDA2KRSXTHR3G5MVUWCONKBYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FTMDA2KRSXTHR3G5MVUWCONKBYY%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLNiuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=8d2f2b55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FTMDA2KRSXTHR3G5MVUWCONKBYY%2F&h=aec73da0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/TMDA2KRSXTHR3G5MVUWCONKBYY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n北戴河會議還有意義嗎？ <br />\n資深傳媒人 - 潘小濤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fyJQHkzjbnL2l_CK9v2fKzXaYzQ=/1111x700/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CBDE76ERGEMTOS7RG5HTKPYKKE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfyJQHkzjbnL2l_CK9v2fKzXaYzQ%3D%2F1111x700%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCBDE76ERGEMTOS7RG5HTKPYKKE.gif&h=b1fe49e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國每年有三個備受關注的政治會議，分別是人大政協「兩會」、北戴河會議、中共中央全會/黨代表大會，不僅是中共用來顯示黨內團結、展示政績，也是外界觀察中共高層互動、路線政策轉變的機會。<br />\n<br />\n每年7月底至8月中的盛夏，中共黨政軍、人大政協等五大系統的領導層成員，退休的黨國元老等，還有部份重要專家等，都會雲集河北秦皇島市的北戴河海邊休養區，部份更偕同家人結伴而來，在此邊度假邊辦公，期間不定期舉行各種非正式會議 （碰頭會），除了重大政策，還會討論高層人事安排。歷史上，中共不少重大決策都在北戴河會議上拍板，包括炮打金門、大躍進等。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。到昨日為止，黨媒上仍未見領導人在北戴河活動的報道，難怪惹來各方揣測，有台灣傳媒報道指北戴河會議已逐漸進入登場狀態，也有外媒質疑今年不會有北戴河會議。<br />\n<br />\n按理，今年是最應召開北戴河會議的。大半個中國被洪水泡浸，除了抗洪，還亟需中央出手賑災；。。。。。。。。。好好討論應對之策。<br />\n<br />\n不過，更大挑戰還是中美關係。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n習李不和浮上枱面<br />\n<br />\n可以說，中美關係陷入死局，除了中國崛起等外部因素，習近平的戰狼外交政策也是主要原因，令西方驚覺中國正在顛覆國際秩序。只要中共高層認真討論一下中美關係，習近平的責任是無法逃避的。但習會讓大家開這樣的會嗎？<br />\n<br />\n而且，習李關係之緊張也是。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。堂堂總理竟遭此羞辱？由此可見，習李兩人已成水火。兩大巨頭關係如此，即使有北戴河會議，大家還能心平氣和坐下來嗎？這樣的北戴河會議，開不開意義已然不大！<br />\n<br />\n潘小濤<br />\n資深傳媒人"},{"pid":"e7c47a1d5afe9373711ba595953dff0786581337","tid":2143418,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"小濤 唔做情浪的一天 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走去邊啊啊啊。整腸仔包？？"},{"pid":"d039068ab001a8b2d5c3d2ab603d901389a2a053","tid":2143418,"uid":108606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7c47a1d5afe9373711ba595953dff0786581337","tid":2143418,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"小濤 唔做情浪的一天 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走去邊啊啊啊。整腸仔包？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:48:23.000Z","msg":"一直想知雞仔坤同菠蘿係邊個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽聲認唔出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf0ec8b92031200f97f4c3180efdcb023a7e22a","tid":2143418,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T06:11:22.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44b1a2a154b8dbb03c89863e6246e688414f61f","tid":2143418,"uid":218494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"今朝聽佢最尾番話，真係聽到眼濕濕，明明聽左咁多年都覺都佢d野唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc3fd45ce9b58199493c8f5310119cab954b924","tid":2143418,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"以住有老毛被推返，今年隨時歷史再現，咁都話北戴河無意義？"}]}